videos.description: Darrel Williams runs for 10 yards on a jet sweep for a LSU touchdown.
videos.headline: Williams takes jet sweep for TD

videos.description: Danny Etling scores LSU's second touchdown on a 13-yard run.
videos.headline: Etling scores on QB keeper

videos.description: Jared Guarantano scrambles and hits Marquez Callaway along the sideline.
videos.headline: Callaway makes toe-tapping catch

videos.description: Jared Guarantano hits Marquez Callaway who takes it 46 yards to the house.
videos.headline: Callaway grabs 46-yard TD

videos.description: Interim head coach Brady Hoke says that they can get by LSU if they continue to play hard in the second half.
videos.headline: Hoke says they can win if they play hard

videos.description: LSU head coach Ed Orgeron has his team excited to play the second half in heavy rain conditions.
videos.headline: Coach O is excited to play in rain

videos.description: The winds are so strong in Knoxville that it moves the ball even when its on the ground.
videos.headline: Heavy winds move ball at line of scrimmage

videos.description: Derrius Guice pounds in a 3-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Guice punches in TD

videos.description: For the second time in the game, Darrel Williams reaches the end zone on a jet sweep.
videos.headline: Williams scores on another jet sweep

videos.description: Jared Guarantano throws to Jeff George who breaks through tackles on his way to a 60-yard gain for the Volunteers.
videos.headline: George breaks tackles for 60-yard gain

videos.description: Bob Wischusen and Brock Huard break down LSU's 30-10 win over Tennessee.
videos.headline: LSU wins in rainy Knoxville

videos.description: With wind wreaking havoc in the first half and rain coming down in the second, the No. 20 Tigers roll to a 30-10 win against the Volunteers.
videos.headline: LSU cruises past Tennessee in tough conditions
